name: DreamscapeArtifact#1
description: The Parallaxicube, stolen from the clutches of the Glitzbeast by Subject J63. Syncope Lab researchers have been unable to produce any results from any experiments. Bearing traits of a hologram even after corporeal materialization. It doesn't respond to touch, produces no tactile sensations, & seemingly cannot be removed from it's point of origin. The board of directors are split, some think ongoing experimentation is necessary, others think returning it to the Glitzbeast will placate it's rage based upon the debriefs provided by Dreamdwellers with experience encountering the beast prior to and after it lost the Parallaxicube
